creator: CoreHR
descriptionHtml:
To use CoreHR, your company must be a CoreHR customer and you must be an authorised user with CoreHR credentials. Not all mobile features may be available to you as you will only have access to what your company has enabled.

ABOUT CoreHR:
CoreHR helps the world’s leading organisations achieve efficiency, high performance, and growth through world-class HCM and Payroll technology. CoreHR manages the complete employee lifecycle, reduces the heavy administration burden on HR teams and delivers exceptional savings in time and money.

CoreHR doesn’t just help your people complete tasks, it transforms how they work and helps create an innovative and engaged workforce that can deliver outstanding success.
descriptionShort: Engage your employees for a better and more productive workplace.
